# Final check for all classes and properties usage:
# Classes:
# noria:CorporateUserIdentifier - Used (AliceSmith, BobJohnson)
# noria:Application - Used (DataFlow, MonitoringSystem)
# noria:ApplicationModule - Used (DataFlowProd, DataFlowDev, MonitoringDev)
# noria:Service - Used (CustomerDataPipeline, InternalMonitoring)
# noria:TroubleTicket - Used (DF_HighCPU, DB_Error)
# noria:TroubleTicketNote - Used (Diagnosis)
# noria:ChangeRequest - Used (DF_Upgrade)
# noria:DocumentAttachment - Used (UpgradePlan)
# noria:EventRecord - Used (HighCPUAlarm, LinkDown, UserLogin, CRStatusChange1, DBError, DBPatchApplied, ServiceRestartCommand, PartyIntervention1, FreezePeriod1)
# noria:AnomalyPattern - Used (MemoryLeak, NetworkCongestion)
# noria:OperationPlan - Used (RestartService, SoftwareUpgrade, TrafficShaping)
# noria:ActionPreCondition - Used (ServiceDegraded, MaintenanceWindow, NetworkCongested)
# noria:ActionPostCondition - Used (ServiceRestored, UpgradeVerified, TrafficNormalized)
# noria:Room - Used (ServerRoom1, NetworkCloset)
# noria:Locus - Used (RackA1, RackA2, RackB1)
# noria:Resource - Used (WebServer01, WebServer02, RouterCore1, VirtualCenter01, DBServer01)
# noria:NetworkInterface - Used (Eth0_WS01, Eth1_WS02, Gig0_CR01, Eth0_DB01)
# noria:NetworkLink - Used (WS01_CR01, WS02_CR01, DB01_CR01)
# noria:ProductModel - Used (DellPowerEdgeR740, CiscoCatalyst9300)
# foaf:Agent (Person) - Used (Alice, Bob, Charlie)
# org:OrganizationalUnit - Used (NetworkOps, AppDev, Dell, Cisco, DBA)
# bot:Site - Used (DataCenterA, OfficeB)
# skos:Concept - Used extensively via noria-kos:

